  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd- \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lankan leaders must engage in urgent action to find long-term solutions - US",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United States has urged Sri Lankan leaders to engage in swift action to find long-term solutions.",
        "The United States has made this request even as the President of Sri Lanka announced his resignation after leaving his official residence.",
        "As the Sri Lankan President prepares to step down, the Sri Lankan Parliament should use this moment to consider its commitment to the betterment of the country and not act on the basis of a single political party, the spokesperson of the US State Department has said.",
        "He appealed to this government or the government that may be elected based on the new constitution to quickly identify and come up with solutions that will bring about long-term economic stability."
      ],
